There are issues about
whether the data are coming

00:35:23.980 --> 00:35:26.700
from households or individuals.

00:35:26.700 --> 00:35:29.590
You have to make
some adjustments

00:35:29.590 --> 00:35:32.700
for household composition.

00:35:32.700 --> 00:35:35.220
And the surveys being used
